bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打陸地戰先係戰狼"},{"pid":"9607b6526b005e394e88c29ba4abb799f712d786","tid":2098740,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:16:15.000Z","msg":"召喚吳京"},{"pid":"3d288a2f0a376f7a6e3f6e5e68b0c959b17b465f","tid":2098740,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:16:48.000Z","msg":"西非海盜違反左國安法，拉得<br />\n戰狼出征，寸草不生，支持核平佢地"},{"pid":"3b24f5df0cca7f3388dfeeb6f303ef82a99ca7f7","tid":2098740,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:17:59.000Z","msg":"衰軟必豬"}]}